                            FEATURED</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Complete Cricket Kit</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Everything you need: bat, pads, gloves, helmet</p>
